name: Personalised Baby Boy Name Card
description:
This card is a perfect keepsake. This card can be personalised with the baby's name and date of birth. Printed on shimmer paper and finished with a diamante. Depending on name length the card size will either be 135x135mm or 180 x 90mm.

Once you have added this to your order and completed payment please send an email by using the 'contact' link on the page with the details required on the card.
